full_text:
All that money and she just walks around town in sweatpants.

Legendary.

#Hawkeye #DisneyPlus

You look nice today.
"What, I don't look nice all the other days?"
"Awww, thanks. You're so sweet."
"Bout f***ing time."

Imaging thinking someone is a good person but also assuming the worst as to their motivations.

Pick a lane.
Watching a cat sleep is peaceful.
